{"tid":589111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【歷史撚】一次大戰時大衞·勞合·喬治同威廉二世有無笑晒口一齊出席宴會","createTime":"2018-03-11T16:16:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-15T08:15:29.000Z","uid":20816,"like":13,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b3dd898a49918b49b0ca514daaeda66380fd80d9","tid":589111,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T16:16:41.000Z","msg":"就好似咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.litenews.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/24775093_2003868722987073_6126012559069880785_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.litenews.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2F24775093_2003868722987073_6126012559069880785_n.jpg&h=b4d80082&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"38a5305ea7c51cfcaf4a9bdada3f0e624d19f849","tid":589111,"uid":20816,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T16:23:00.000Z","msg":"民主派批評立法會草草通過修訂議事規則聲言百倍奉還<br />\n15.12.2017 19:22<br />\n<br />\n立法會表決通過建制派提出的議事規則修訂後，民主派議員晚上一齊見記者。民主派會議召集人莫乃光批評，立法會草草通過議事規則修訂，民主派會向建制派百倍奉還，並會注視建制派今後會否用這種手段，推動各種惡法，包括二十三條立法。公民黨黨魁楊岳橋承認，民主派輸了這場<span style=\"color: red;\">戰役</span>，但是輸了給主席及不公平的制度。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨主席胡志偉質疑是特區政府放水，「打籠通」，通過修改議事規則可以令政府提出的惡法、工程項目等政策，都能草草通過，減低面對群眾的壓力。香港本土的毛孟靜指，民主派的抗爭意志，今後只會更堅定，力量更強大。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_341&amp;itemid=982376\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3Fcsid%3D261_341%26itemid%3D982376&d=ZU%2BVxSsGslah%2F71SpSkvf8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=3adfb342\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_341&amp;itemid=982376</a>"},{"pid":"9e0c5bc0e515a5db23fbcfef89a3f4632ff6f3c1","tid":589111,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T04:07:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac56d5497c42fc64888990ba81bc9767fe089b84","tid":589111,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":